rows.label: tlk45100251_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey listen, me and my mum and dad
are all moving to Acedia soon!

rows.label: tlk45100251_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Hmm... I wonder if you can get Cloud
Sea Crab Sticks in Acedia too?

rows.label: tlk45100251_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Having to leave all my friends behind
is bad, but having to leave my favorite
foods behind would be even worse...

rows.label: tlk45100251_01_msg0005
rows.name:
I heard when a country's business is
booming, they trade more with other
places and you can get imported goods!

rows.label: tlk45100251_01_msg0006
rows.name:
So we just have to buy lots of stuff
and make business in Acedia do great!
